# S03-T07: Modular Widget Layout

## Objective
Build the HUD slot-based widget container system enabling future drag-and-drop (S05-T06).

## Acceptance Criteria
- `src/features/hud/layout/WidgetSlot.tsx` represents one of 7 slots (TL, TC, TR, ML, MR, BL, BR).
- `src/features/hud/layout/WidgetRegistry.ts` maps widget id → component.
- `useLayoutStore` persists per-slot widget id + visibility flag (localStorage).
- Slots support 1+ widgets stacked vertically with gap-y-2.

## Steps
1. Define slot layout in `AppShell` (from S01-T10).
2. Build `<WidgetSlot>` with motion mount/unmount (Framer 200ms).
3. Define widget registry contract.
4. Implement persistence layer.

## Invariants
- Slots fixed in count (7) — no dynamic slot creation.
- Widget swap does not unmount slot wrapper.
- Center video area protected — no slot draws over it.
